{
  "title": "Crispy Chinese Pineapple Skewers",
  "description": "A buttery and flaky Chinese dish featuring a mix of fruit, perfect for crowds and grill lovers, with no onions or garlic. This dish is a crowd pleaser and can be served as a snack or dessert.",
