  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium heat.",
    "Thread the fruit chunks onto skewers.",
    "Roll out the flaky pastry dough to a thickness of about 1/8 inch.",
    "Cut the pastry dough into strips about 1 inch wide.",
    "Wrap each skewer with a strip of pastry dough, brushing with melted butter.",
    "Brush the tops of the pastry with the beaten egg.",
    "Sprinkle the tops with sugar and salt.",
    "Grill the skewers for about 5 minutes on each side, or until the pastry is golden brown.",
    "Serve the skewers hot and enjoy."
  ],
